-Sweet!

568
00:43:04.873 --> 00:43:06.625
Yeah.

569
00:43:07.334 --> 00:43:08.419
Ah. shit.

570
00:43:09.420 --> 00:43:12.339
Much appreciated!

571
00:43:13.882 --> 00:43:17.177
